  "detailed_description": "<h1>Puppy Park Announcement</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/378db65e21fec844a5399887566617f4.avif?t=1758237014\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new dinosaurs in booster packs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/54188f8285760248cd069c0bafdf6e78.poster.avif?t=1758237014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/54188f8285760248cd069c0bafdf6e78.webm?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/54188f8285760248cd069c0bafdf6e78.mp4?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your dinosaurs to increase their income and sale value!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/8d02b9b955124c4e8da4c7093f5c303d.poster.avif?t=1758237014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/8d02b9b955124c4e8da4c7093f5c303d.webm?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/8d02b9b955124c4e8da4c7093f5c303d.mp4?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breed your dinosaurs together to discover super rare variants!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/96ccab266080c254f7ac00a90dfcded1.poster.avif?t=1758237014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/96ccab266080c254f7ac00a90dfcded1.webm?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/96ccab266080c254f7ac00a90dfcded1.mp4?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your park at the shop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/094117ed2c14eda22e5362531d48067c.poster.avif?t=1758237014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/094117ed2c14eda22e5362531d48067c.webm?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/094117ed2c14eda22e5362531d48067c.mp4?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you collect them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/0c98e12a46ef0fdc7087aba5fa42d212.poster.avif?t=1758237014\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795380/extras/0c98e12a46ef0fdc7087aba5fa42d212.webm?t=1758237014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_